with a place to pray.

25:28.840 --> 25:30.120
Why don't you tell the rabbi that?

25:30.120 --> 25:31.360
I will.

25:31.360 --> 25:33.840
Of all the absurd...

25:33.840 --> 25:35.280
And don't tell me
how to run my hospital.

25:35.280 --> 25:37.200
And don't tell me
how to run my hospital.

25:37.200 --> 25:39.440
