of your hospital.

25:39.440 --> 25:41.240
Don't do that. Katharine!

25:41.240 --> 25:42.560
PLATE SHATTERS

25:42.560 --> 25:44.000
Happy anniversary.

25:44.000 --> 25:48.000
Same to you.

25:49.600 --> 25:53.600
And your mother sent soup.

25:55.120 --> 25:57.400
Are they giving you
enough drugs?

25:57.400 --> 26:00.400
They don't  have
enough drugs.

26:00.400 --> 26:03.080
My son, shot. This is
unbelievable to me.

26:03.080 --> 26:06.360
Candy.

26:06.360 --> 26:08.400
None of these
are on my diet.

26:08.400 --> 26:11.480
