all the time.

29:48.040 --> 29:52.040
We always knew
where we stood
with each other.

29:52.440 --> 29:54.760
I guess I want reassurance
that this is the right thing.

29:54.760 --> 29:57.640
I guess I want reassurance
that this is the right thing.

29:57.640 --> 29:59.560
We owe you a lot, Donald.

29:59.560 --> 30:01.480
A member of our family

30:01.480 --> 30:04.160
is going to be
somebody important.

30:04.160 --> 30:05.760
A doctor. Because of you.

30:05.760 --> 30:08.400
No, what Carol's done,
she's done on her own.

30:08.400 --> 30:09.640
