31:38.880 --> 31:40.680
Very little.

31:40.680 --> 31:43.040
No. The men in power
protect each other.

31:43.040 --> 31:45.000
It's out of loyalty,
not malice,

31:45.000 --> 31:47.120
but still, no excuse.

31:47.120 --> 31:51.000
I'm sorry to lose one of the
few women of influence here.

31:51.000 --> 31:53.400
I left my family
in Maryland

31:53.400 --> 31:56.000
for the opportunity to come
and run the department.

31:56.000 --> 31:58.240
I can be a surgeon
closer to home.

31:58.240 --> 32:00.200
I'd still like to see
you fighting.

32:00.200 --> 32:01.640
Be wasted energy.

32:01.640 --> 32:04.160
Oh! &gt;

32:04.160 --> 32:07.120
Aah!

32:07.120 --> 32:11.120
Besides, I think Mark Craig
deserves his office back.

32:24.880 --> 32:28.880
Rabbi, I'm Daniel Auschlander,
Chief of Services.

32:31.960 --> 32:33.360
I was about to begin my prayers.

32:33.360 --> 32:36.640
