TANNOY ANNOUNCEMENT

43:50.920 --> 43:54.920
LIFT PINGS

44:02.920 --> 44:06.200
Seems like we'll
be working together...

44:06.200 --> 44:10.200
very closely.

44:21.440 --> 44:23.280
Well, there you are.

44:23.280 --> 44:24.360
Leaving?

44:24.360 --> 44:25.800
All through for the day.

44:25.800 --> 44:29.800
Let me help you.

44:30.960 --> 44:33.960
Katharine, about today.

44:33.960 --> 44:37.960
I'm sorry.

44:41.000 --> 44:43.680
"Excuse me...

44:43.680 --> 44:45.800
"could you please tell me
where in this town

44:45.800 --> 44:49.800
"they mix a good
old-fashioned egg cream?"

44:50.560 --> 44:53.480
Then you said...

44:53.480 --> 44:56.040
"Come on."

44:56.040 --> 44:58.120
And then you said...

44:58.120 --> 45:00.960
"I haven't had
an egg cream in years."

45:00.960 --> 45:04.840
And...

45:04.840 --> 45:06.760
"I'm sure you'd get one

45:06.760 --> 45:10.600
"at Hobson's
on Franklin Street.

45:10.600 --> 45:13.480
"You take Essex
to Tremont...

45:13.480 --> 45:15.720
"..turn right,
go three blocks,

45:15.720 --> 45:19.320
"and it's just across
the way from the cyclorama.

45:19.320 --> 45:21.040
"Wait a moment.

45:21.040 --> 45:23.520
"Turn right on Essex,
go two blocks and then?

45:23.520 --> 45:25.120
"Oh, never mind.

45:25.120 --> 45:27.400
"You want me
to show you?

45:27.400 --> 45:29.920
"That would be lovely."

